            <p class="home-text text-justify">
              Brancart & Brancart is a civil rights law firm dedicated to enforcing the Fair Housing Act and similar laws throughout the United States. Since 1989, the firm has represented thousands of individuals who have experienced housing discrimination based on race, color, national origin, religion, sex, the presence of children, sexual orientation, marital status, source of income, or disability. 
            </p>

            <p class="home-text text-justify">
              The firm also provides education, training and support to fair housing advocates and attorneys throughout the United States.
            </p>

            <p class="home-text text-justify">
              <b>The firm accepts clients by referral only from fair housing agencies.</b> If you believe you have been the victim of housing discrimination, please contact <a href="links">your local fair housing agency.</a>
            </p>

